@Golden_Pup These count IF your doctor classifies them as such. A few years ago, I was otherwise healthy getting my flu shot. 40 mins later, I had debilitating nerve pain that lasted several wks. Was told it was shingles (no scabbing - just intense pain on my left side, where I got shot) 🤷‍♀️

@Golden_Pup Thank you so much! Confirmed my worst fears for sure. 10x as many incidents of myocarditis for those under 18 as there were actual covid deaths (with or of covid). Only 14 covid deaths under 19. Over 100 myocarditis cases. Absolutely disgusting and criminal. But I appreciate you!
@Golden_Pup And still the stupid message pops up saying why "health officials" dont agree 🙄

@Golden_Pup Ontario goverment table misleading eh?
Come on @Twitter this is official data...if official data is misleading please tell me whats not misleading
